</P>
<P>
   WASHINGTON-MOTTO (Washington) _ If all goes as planned, new
vehicle tags in the nation's capital will soon be emblazoned with
the phrase ``Taxation without Representation.'' By Anne E.
Kornblut. 1080 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR;  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   RELIGION-BOYS (Undated) _ The Catholic bishops of the United
States have agreed to help rescue the so-called ``lost boys'' of
the Sudan, resettling American cities several thousand orphaned and
wounded young men who fled a brutal civil war. By Michael Paulson.
1100 words. (a and i coding)
</P>
<P>
