comes next?
</P>
<P>
   Are the SLA's enemies now going to dig up the dead? Already, the
Hezbollah are erecting their ``memorials,'' banners at the site of
each guerrilla ambush, listing the name of each anti-Israeli
suicide bomber and the date of his death.
</P>
<P>
   In days to come, it's possible their enemies will destroy those
banners too. And one comes back to the old Lebanese question: if
you do what the bad guys do, what is the difference between you and
them? &QL; 
