<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-12 14:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9971 &Cx1f; taf-z
u v AM-NYT-BUDGET &LR;      07-12 1554
