<P>
   CHAMPLAIN-CANCEL (Undated) _ Students and coaches at Champlain
College, a small liberal arts school that has long dominated
basketball and soccer national championships, are miffed over the
administration's decision to cancel all varsity sports. By David
Abel. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
