<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-12 18:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0269 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r e BC-FORLOVE-OFMUSIC-1800(     07-12 0799
