<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-FOOD-CRAVINGS-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
A CRAVING IS A CRAVING
</HEADLINE>
  (For use after July 17, 2000, by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By EVAN HENERSON 
c.2000 Los Angeles Daily News 
<TEXT>
<P>
   It creeps up on you, ringing the tiniest of bells in your ear. A
