</P>
<P>
   ``We don't think it's in the region's interest to see that
technology introduced,'' said White House foreign policy spokesman
P.J. Crowley.
</P>
<P>
   In a letter sent to inform Chinese President Jiang Zemin of the
suspension, Barak cited this week's peace talks, saying the
